<title>VTE 2.91 Widget Example</title>
<p>
This example demonstrates use of
the <link href="https://developer-old.gnome.org/vte/stable/">VTE 2.91 widget</link> API
in an application.
</p>
<p>
Also, this example demonstrates use of other GTK widgets:
</p>
<list style="compact">
<item><p><link href="https://developer-old.gnome.org/gtk3/stable/GtkMessageDialog.html">message dialog</link></p></item>
<item><p><link href="https://developer-old.gnome.org/gtk3/stable/GtkFontChooserDialog.html">font chooser dialog</link></p></item>
<item>
  <p>
    <link href="https://developer-old.gnome.org/gtk3/stable/GtkButton.html">button</link>,
    with a <link href="https://developer-old.gnome.org/gio/stable/GSimpleAction.html">simple action</link>
    that is added to an <link href="https://developer-old.gnome.org/gio/stable/GActionMap.html">action map</link>
  </p>
</item>
<item><p><link href="https://developer-old.gnome.org/gtk3/stable/GtkSpinButton.html">spin button</link></p></item>
</list>

<section>
<title>Download</title>
